text-align:center;\"|0.242\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Did Not Qualify\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Quarter Finals ([[BBL Trophy|BT]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1st Round ([[BBL Cup|BC]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Gavin Love]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2018\u201319 British Basketball League season|2018\u201319]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''[[British Basketball League|BBL]]'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|I\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8th\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|33\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|16\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|32\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|0.485\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Semi Finals, losing to [[Leicester Riders|Leicester]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Quarter Finals ([[BBL Trophy|BT]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Quarter Finals ([[BBL Cup|BC]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Paul James (basketball)|Paul James]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2019\u201320 British Basketball League season|2019\u201320]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''[[British Basketball League|BBL]]'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|I\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Paul James (basketball)|Paul James]]\n|}\n\n==Players==\n===Retired numbers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"{{Basketball color cell|Plymouth Raiders}};\"| Plymouth Raiders retired numbers\n|-\n! style=\"{{Basketball color cell2| Plymouth Raiders}};\"|No.\n! style=\"{{Basketball color cell2| Plymouth Raiders}};\"|{{Tooltip|Nat.|Nationality}}\n! style=\"{{Basketball color cell2| Plymouth Raiders}};\"|Player\n! style=\"{{Basketball color cell2| Plymouth Raiders}};\"|Position\n! style=\"{{Basketball color cell2| Plymouth Raiders}};\"|Tenure\n|-\n| width=50 | '''6''' || {{flagicon|UK}} || style=\"text-align:left;\" width=150 | [[Gavin Love]] || [[Guard (basketball)|G]] ||  1996\u20132009\n|-\n| width=50 | '''14''' || {{flagicon|UK}} || style=\"text-align:left;\" width=150 | [[Gary Stronach]] || [[Guard (basketball)|G]] ||  1985\u20131999\n|}\n\n===Current roster===\n<section begin=roster />{{Basketball roster nationality note}}\n{{Basketball roster header|wt=n|age=n\n| team=Plymouth Raiders\n}}<!-- list of players -->\n{{player3 | num = 2 | nat = GBR | first = Tola | last = Okiki | pos = PG | ft = 6 | in = 2 }}\n{{player3 | num = 3 | nat = USA | first = Tyrell | last = Johnson | dab = basketball | pos = SF | ft = 6 | in = 8 }}\n{{player3 | num = 4 | nat = AUS | first = Joshua | last = Wilcher | pos = PG | ft = 5 | in = 10 }}\n{{player3 | num = 7 | nat = FRA | first = Ron | last = Mvouika | pos = SG | ft = 6 | in = 5 }}\n{{player3 | num = 8 | nat = GBR | first = Liam | last = Langridge-Barker | pos = SG | ft = 6 | in = 5 }}\n{{player3 | num = 9 | nat = GBR | first = Isaiah | last = Walker | pos = SF | ft = 6 | in = 5 }}\n{{player3 | num = 10 | nat = GBR | first = Denzel | last = Ubiaro | pos = SF | ft = 6 | in = 3 }}\n{{player3 | num = 11 | nat = BVI | first = Leslee | last = Smith | pos = PF | ft = 6 | in = 8 }}\n{{player3 | num = 12 | nat = LTU | first = Kostas | last = Jonu\u0161ka  | pos = SG | ft = 6 | in = 5 }}\n{{player3 | num = 13 | nat = GBR | first = Isa | last = Brandon | pos = PG | ft = 6 | in = 4 }}\n{{player3 | num = 15 | nat = USA | first = Samuel | last = Daniel | pos = SF | ft = 6 | in = 8 }}\n{{player3 | num = 21 | nat = GBR | first = Theo | last = Turner | pos = C | ft = 7 | in = 0 }}\n{{player3 | num = 22 | nat = USA | first = Rashad | last = Hassan | pos = PF | ft = 6 | in = 8 }}\n{{player3 | num = 32 | nat = GBR | first = Joshua | last = Palmer  | pos = PG | ft = 6 | in = 3 }}\n<!-- end list of players -->\n{{Ba